ActExcise Act, 2001
PrecisREGULATIONS RESPECTING THE INFORMATION TO BE DISPLAYED ON ALCOHOL CONTAINERS AND THEIR PACKAGING which prescribe the information that must be displayed on alcohol containers and their packaging (i.e., the name, address and licence number of the licensee who packaged it), and take effect on July 1, 2003.
